{"tid":1972485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獅城港人戴口罩受盡歧視","createTime":"2020-04-14T14:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T20:35:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf4148066504318a8539d5675f596935bd5ce58","tid":1972485,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200414/6RZTG3XORDN447KL5SAALXAZ6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200414%2F6RZTG3XORDN447KL5SAALXAZ6I%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWclSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=5145a0e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200414%2F6RZTG3XORDN447KL5SAALXAZ6I%2F&h=06501a86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200414/6RZTG3XORDN447KL5SAALXAZ6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n獅城港人戴口罩受盡歧視<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200414/large/1586794046_8984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586794046_8984.jpg&h=1dc847e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港人Eros<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新加坡政府一直不建議國民外出戴口罩，高官認為只在患病時才須佩戴。直至本月初，當局才不反對國民在公開場所戴口罩，及後幾日內變成鼓勵、再變成規定要戴口罩。新加坡一直是港人移民熱點，但這陣子港人在那裏並不好受；疫潮初期他們戴口罩外出被歧視，有港人索性回港。<br />\n<br />\n上班族曾被迫除罩<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：瑪嘉烈負壓房故障 涉69病人<br />\n<br />\n「爆發有好多原因，1月到3月市民被告知『冇病唔使戴口罩』，可能係其中一個」。fb專頁「透視新加坡」港人總編輯Eric說：「初時喺條街度或者office戴口罩會俾人歧視，啲人話要信WHO、戴口罩要Responsible（要留給醫護勿浪費），甚至會被問候係咪有病，病就返屋企休息，我哋WhatsApp group內亦有朋友嘅公司同學校逼人除罩。到今個月頭先話唔反對戴口罩，仲派棉口罩，早兩日先出政策叫大家一定要戴」。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡疫情其中一個致命傷是外勞，單是周日錄得141宗外勞確診。Eric說：「始終新加坡太倚賴外勞，建築裝修、剪草、清潔、飲食零售、送遞等尤其重要。外勞本身住埋一個宿舍，佢哋又會喺啲人口密集社區度買嘢，但同時要做清潔維持潔淨市容，周圍走嚟走去。新加坡市容潔淨唔代表衞生意識高，加上頭幾個月習慣唔戴口罩，少消毒，容易互相傳播。」<br />\n<br />\n另一位港人「獅家星探」Eros形容，現時當地氣氛嚴肅，她昨外出攝製節目時，「係冇人講嘢㗎，好靜囉，個心有啲唔舒服」。她聽聞不少新加坡港人對政府有微言，不滿抗疫措施推得遲。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡港人應如何自處，Eric指身邊的港人一直無懼歧視，堅持戴口罩勤消毒，而有些朋友則已返港，他自己則絕少外出。"},{"pid":"c97f198a868e0e088ee23c5cb3119aa6ebf58cd6","tid":1972485,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"Monkeys see monkeys do<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHuman trust monkeys <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89525d96f39baf8968515c640649d20e890f909f","tid":1972485,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CrXRXgm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrXRXgm.png&h=0cd9708f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9343b7a515361ed6f9325c86ffa2b639ba2e12c","tid":1972485,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97f198a868e0e088ee23c5cb3119aa6ebf58cd6","tid":1972485,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"Monkeys see monkeys do<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHuman trust monkeys <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"Monkey sick monkey die"},{"pid":"7fa11aa990568c8c00602d3e560d762eeae361ee","tid":1972485,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9343b7a515361ed6f9325c86ffa2b639ba2e12c","tid":1972485,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97f198a868e0e088ee23c5cb3119aa6ebf58cd6","tid":1972485,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"Monkeys see monkeys do<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHuman trust monkeys <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"Monkey sick monkey die"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"Monkey cry, monkey buy<br />\nmonkey say goodbye"},{"pid"